<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head prefix="og: https://ogp.me/ns# fb: https://ogp.me/ns/fb# website: https://ogp.me/ns/website#">
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
<!--meta http-equiv="refresh" content="15; url=https://www.hbc.co.jp/"-->
<title>404 ページが見つかりません｜HBC北海道放送</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/image/favicon.ico">
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/image/apple-touch-icon.png">
<style>
  *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body,h1,h2,h3,h4,p,ul,ol{margin:0}
  body{min-height:100vh;text-rendering:optimizeSpeed;word-break:break-all}
  ul,ol{padding:0}
  html {font-size:62.5%}
  body {
    background:#f1f1f1;
    color:#181818;
    font-family:"Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", "Hiragino Sans", Meiryo, sans-serif;
    font-size:1.6rem;
    line-height:2.0;
    -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;
    text-size-adjust:100%;
  }
  a {color:#1558d6}
  a:visited {color:#681da8}
  a:hover, a:active {color:#44a0ff}
  a.btn {
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
    width:90%;
    max-width:290px;
    height:60px;
    margin:1.2rem auto;
    padding:0 1.6em;
    border:1px solid #d80024;
    border-radius:100vh;
    background:#ffffff;
    color:#d80024;
    font-size:1.7rem;
    font-weight:bold;
    text-decoration:none;
    transition:0.2s;
  }
  a.btn:hover, a.btn:active {background:#d80024; color:#ffffff}
  a.btn::after {
    content:'';
    display:block;
    width:14px;
    height:38px;
    background-image:url(https://www.hbc.co.jp/image/icon_btn_arrow_red.svg), url(https://www.hbc.co.jp/image/icon_btn_arrow_w.svg);
    background-position:center center;
    background-repeat:no-repeat;
    background-size:14px auto, 0;
  }
  a.btn:hover::after, a.btn:active::after {background-size:0, 14px auto}
  .contents {
    width:90%;
    max-width:800px;
    margin:15% auto;
    text-align:center;
  }
  .error h1 {
    margin-bottom:9%;
    color:#2A71E8;
    font-size:clamp(3.2rem, 9.3vw, 5.8rem);
    line-height:1.0;
  }
  .error h1 .code {
    margin-right:0.25em;
    font-size:1.04em;
    letter-spacing:0.1em;
  }
  .error p {margin-bottom:1.8em}
  .error p.current span {display:inline-block}
  .recommend {
    margin-top:15%;
    padding:5%;
    border-radius:5px;
    box-shadow:0 0 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    background:#fff;
  }
  .recommend h2 {font-size:clamp(2.0rem, 5.0vw, 2.4rem)}
  .recommend ul {list-style:none}
  .recommend li {margin-top:0.5em}
  footer {
    padding:15px 0;
    background:#292929;
    color:#fff;
    font-size:1.2rem;
    text-align:center;
  }
  address {
    font:inherit;
    line-height:20px;
  }
  @media print, screen and (min-width:600px) {
    .contents {margin:10% auto}
    .error h1 {margin-bottom:6%}
    .recommend {margin-top:10%; padding:4%}
  }
  @media print, screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    footer {padding:25px 0}
  }
  @media print, screen and (min-width:960px) {
    body {font-size:1.8rem}
    .contents {margin:130px auto}
    .error h1 {font-size:6.2rem}
    .recommend h2 {font-size:2.7rem}
  }
</style>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.hbc.co.jp/css/top/g_menu.css"/>
<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<meta http-equiv="refresh" content="15; url=https://www.hbc.co.jp/">
<!-- Google Tag Manager -->
<script>(function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':
new Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],
j=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=
'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);
})(window,document,'script','dataLayer','GTM-5XPXCVX');</script>
<!-- End Google Tag Manager -->
</head>
<body>
<!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
<noscript><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-5XPXCVX"
height="0" width="0" style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript>
<!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
<nav>
	<script src="https://www.hbc.co.jp/java_scripts/g_menu_s.js"></script>
	<script src="https://www.hbc.co.jp/java_scripts/g_menu_script.js"></script>
</nav>
<div class="contents">
  <div class="error">
    <h1><span class="code">404</span>Not Found</h1>
    <p>申し訳ありません。<br>指定されたページは準備中または削除されたため、現在ご覧いただけません。</p>
    <p>このページは15秒後にHBCトップページへ移動します。<br>移動しない場合はボタンをクリックしてください。
    <a href="https://www.hbc.co.jp" class="btn">HBCトップページへ</a></p>
  </div>
</div>
<footer>
  <address>
  <script src="https://www.hbc.co.jp/java_scripts/copyright.js"></script></address>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
